      <title>欧元区通胀问题不太可能阻止欧洲央行降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/a-euro-zone-inflation-hiccup-is-unlikely-to-thwart-ecb-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本月欧元区通胀可能回升，但不太可能破坏欧洲央行即将大幅降息的计划。]]></description>
