      <title>石油公司债务上限威胁后哥伦比亚债券和比索下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/colombia-bonds-peso-drop-after-petro-threats-over-debt-ceiling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗威胁称，如果立法者拒绝批准提高该国债务上限，他将“停止付款”，导致哥伦比亚债券和货币暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/colombia-bonds-peso-drop-after-petro-threats-over-debt-ceiling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 15:03:26 GMT</pubDate>
