      <title>内格尔表示欧洲央行应等到 9 月份才进行第二次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/nagel-says-ecb-should-wait-for-september-to-do-second-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行行长约阿希姆·内格尔表示，欧洲央行在 6 月份开始降低借贷成本后，可能应该等到 9 月份再进行后续降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/nagel-says-ecb-should-wait-for-september-to-do-second-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 14:24:48 GMT</pubDate>
